      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GLENEAGLE RULER (1) has been racing well of late. Drew on the back row and finished fifth at his latest appearance at Blayney to follow a string of top-two finishes. Likely to get all the favours from the ace draw. REBOUNDER (3) drew wide in a higher-graded race last start so there was merit in his effort for fifth. Came from this barrier to win in this company here prior. Has winning claims. WHERE BACK (4) has had four weeks off since a fresh win at Goulburn but has been kept up to the mark with a nice trial. Up in grade but won the only time she raced here so is one of the main contenders. SHAZADELE (10) may need a bit of luck from the tricky draw but her form is strong including a win two back and a nose second last week.",
